<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='123000' id='t-123000'>and you have a loved one</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='125000' id='t-125000'>who has blockages in two coronary arteries</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='128000' id='t-128000'>and your family doctor refers
