<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='131000' id='t-131000'>who's batting 200 on angioplasties.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='135000' id='t-135000'>But, but, you know what?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='137000' id='t-137000'>She's doing a lot better this year.
