<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='193310' id='t-193310'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='196000' id='t-196000'>And so I did.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='198000' id='t-198000'>And I studied in my little garret</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='200000' id='t-200000'>at the nurses' residence
