<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='235453' id='t-235453'>or as much as possible,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='237000' id='t-237000'>as close to everything as possible,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='239000' id='t-239000'>that it would immunize me
