<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='242000' id='t-242000'>And it worked</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='244000' id='t-244000'>for a while,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='247000' id='t-247000'>until I met Mrs. Drucker.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='250000' id='t-250000'>I was a resident at a teaching
